      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content
</head>
         <p>Percy writes about the National Book Awards, comments on Hnery James' <title render="italic">The golden bowl</title> and Stafford's <title render="italic">A mother in history,</title> compliments a story by
her, and mentions his uncle, a stay at Key West, and current activities and feelings.
</p>
      </scopecontent>
